<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Shovel of Ponz Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Talk to Vira in the Temple of Solusek Ro<BR>
to obtain the quest.<BR>
<BR>
2) Get a toe from a Hill giant<BR>
<BR>
3) Get a shovel from magicians in Najena or Cazic Thule<BR>
<BR>
4) Get the eyes of a gargoyle.<BR>
<BR>
5) Buy a ruby in a shop<BR>
<BR>
6) Give all 4 items to Vira to obtain the Shovel of Ponz.</div>
<BR>
